You can simply just add `margin-bottom` when the hover takes place. This way, when the user hovers over the image, a margin-bottom will take place which will push the text below.

Try this:


&lt;!-- begin snippet: js hide: false console: true babel: false --&gt;

&lt;!-- language: lang-css --&gt;

